headline: Better Stock-Split Stock: Fastenal, O'Reilly Automotive, or Interactive Brokers?
summary: Fastenal is the easy pick for income investors among these three stock-split stocks.  Value investors probably won't like any of these stocks, although Interactive Brokers has the lowest forward earnings multiple.  Growth investors will likely prefer O'Reilly Automotive.

headline: Is O'Reilly Automotive Stock a Millionaire Maker?
summary: O'Reilly Automotive is a fast-growing auto parts retailer.  O'Reilly has seen many notable stock price pullbacks in its history.  Shares of O'Reilly Automotive (NASDAQ: ORLY) have risen more than 200% over the past five years.
